Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:11.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こそばゆいけど耳かして　嗫いた本气だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:18.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ナゾカケーホラーエンジン発进　いま决めたアイになれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:26.02,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とまらないよね　でも最高　鸣り响く胜利のベル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:33.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}平和にさえ勇气ひつよう　目指すのは未知の空路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:40.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}调子イイね拍子拔け　答えが残念だって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:50.16,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大スキになっちゃうよ　悔しくココロ骚いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:55.06,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}憧れのMOON LIGHT　远くて茫然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.83,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}シアワセだって窗越える
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:02.14,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}HIGH LIGHT　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:06.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}落ち着かない恋の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:16.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}试练は可怜にパスして　もうだいじょうぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:11.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然有点痒  但还是把耳朵凑近点  轻声嘟嚷自己是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:18.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}猜谜  闹鬼  引擎发动  化为刚定下来的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:26.02,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}已经无法阻止  但这种感觉很棒不是吗  胜利之钟声响彻长空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:33.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}太平世界仍需勇气  目标是未知的航空路线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:40.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}状态很好  真没想到  得到的回覆令人遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:50.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}变得更加喜欢了  心脏就如小鹿乱涨  有点不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:55.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}憧憬的MOON LIGHT  既遥远又模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸福也能透过窗户
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:02.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}HIGH LIGHT  直到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:06.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无法平静的恋情  直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:16.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}华丽地通过试炼  已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:08.45,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}You always wish upon stars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:12.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}I don't know what you long for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:18.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}Because everything that I need is here by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:23.04,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}We named some stars out of reach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.67,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}Listened to the wind sung
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:30.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We are little kids but
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:33.52,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We know what is worth for us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.43,0:22:38.31,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Someday you'll find that what you've been longing for is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:41.85,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Here in this small town you don't like
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:49.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Someday I say the words I've never said to anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:52.59,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}You make me smile，make me cry，
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:56.26,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Make me feel that I can fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:23:02.69,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Sure you belong to me like I belong to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:03.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I said，
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:09.50,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}"I'm on your side even when you are wrong"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:13.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I wanna be your hero to save you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:21.51,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}From everything that hurt you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始移植核心  你有什么话要我转告给米利安姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那个…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆大概会生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.03,0:00:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这不算是为了米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我想这么做才这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了米利安姆小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是因为我想把我的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把魂白珠送给米利安姆所以才给她的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我要说的就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让她变成健康的米利安姆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  被叫姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:29.20,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,270)\fad(1000,0)}各自的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:29.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,270)\fad(1000,0)}各自的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米内特  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜  米内特她！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家也都在找她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔跟我从天上找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙缇  你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力搜查开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林地区查到疑似米内特小姐的魂白珠的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速赶往那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速启动  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干哦  雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有强力的艾尔反应接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙缇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你们过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙缇  把雷斯塔送到有反应的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都是依赖着雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次就由我来让你依赖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法发动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您武运昌盛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就由我来拖住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑得快的对手就用数量来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都让她躲过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现强大的圣者遗物的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得太美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象无伤  攻击被无效化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像个猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武技强大  还有战斗用的圣者遗物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为胜利几率非常低
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很强  不能就这么放过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明得快点赶回去…立刻了结她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的被她预料到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件反射  刚才是以她的直觉来回避的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难缠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挺强的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你有想要保护的人  我一样有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  所以我不会留手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然来了吗  雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝丁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把米内特还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝丁  如果我站在你的立场上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许会跟你选择同一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要是你站在现在的我的立场上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定会像我一样做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们的路就不会相容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要让它们相容的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚脐要给抢走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了莉特丝  表情那么严肃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  只是想起只有姐姐的衣服还晾在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的也收回去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿溜溜的姐姐不是很性感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想洗过的衣服还湿溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这种事  还是快赶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶紧把那件事告诉大家才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要拯救米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想妨碍的话  我就不会放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗用圣者遗物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我和阿薇莉尔为了战斗而在体内装了好几个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你没事啊米内特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  为什么  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米内特  这很危险你稍微退后些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是爸爸  为了女儿我可以豁出一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是爸爸  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真考虑之后得出自己的结论了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懂事  米内特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不怪我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果米内特认真考虑过的话  我不会怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我的选择却不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的…选择？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  还有阿薇莉尔  现在都非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不只要拯救米内特和米利安姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要拯救阿贝丁和阿薇莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救我们？天真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要硬着来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要全部救下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痴人说梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打算当它是梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以为了要实现  就得先让眼前的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打倒我吗  雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  助我一臂之力吧  阿贝丁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有何能耐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然打破了艾尔的防御
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝丁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝丁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雷斯塔在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙缇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贝丁大人  米利安姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想同归于尽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事  米内特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米内特  我也很任性和贪心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的东西就不择手段去得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不只是我  卡莉娜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有切露西  阿尼艾丝  尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连尼娜也是  大家都是任性  贪心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  米内特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想和米利安姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和阿贝丁  阿薇莉尔小姐  还有米内特在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米内特也可以跟我们一起企望得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以任性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊  别自己一个人烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是觉得辛苦的话  可以向我们委托任务哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  米内特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和爸爸  和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和米利安姆一起得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米内特…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和哥哥  和大家永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种状态就别走出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哥哥你们每次都会帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没让你感到痛苦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身边总有着哥哥  有着阿薇莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有新的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样一直支撑着我的双手  我知道他们非常善良
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有愿意把重要的核心送给我的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比这更幸福的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  米内特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆小姐  阿贝丁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  你受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  因为我控制力道正好不会造成重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米内特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米内特就算我不愿意也要把核心送给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我希望米利安姆能健康起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后哥哥和阿薇莉尔为了我要将米内特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…那个…已经不想再看到米利安姆小姐受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而Oasis的各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我们希望能听到米利安姆小姐的真正心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我把我的真正心意  把我的任性传达给各位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死  我想和哥哥还有大家永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以雷斯塔先生  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  阿贝丁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现我们的任性要求吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这委托我们接下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  就和这工会联手  一起寻找方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆小姐  米内特姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挤过去也没人会怪你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达成和解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿薇莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米利安姆小姐  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该谢谢阿薇莉尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和阿薇莉尔在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米内特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起让你们担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可不是你们上演和谐一幕的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加内特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情一会再说  快回Oasis  出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧大家一起冲回去吧  出大事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  真是出大事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天上突然哆啪地冒出光来  叭叭地流到山里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后晶石怪物哗啦哗啦的  太吓人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上为调查结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提报酬请用雷斯塔自身来支付
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从天上铺下来的光之道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是从天盖的水车向卫星的逆流的艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界末日即将降临  哈米吉多顿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从天盖的水车？阿贝哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是师父所在之地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能现在正发生什么重大变故
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安定世间艾尔的东西发生异常了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  情况非常紧迫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔乱流  晶石怪物暴走  数量越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话不仅是埃尔塔利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个世界都会被晶石怪物袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是所谓的世界危机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  如果米利安姆的核心异常也是天盖的水车造成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决它的话  米利安姆就会好起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  就算没有好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也或许会找得到救米利安姆的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  阿贝哥  阿薇莉尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那米内特在这真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂白珠是能安定艾尔的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能在解决天盖的水车的暴走时起作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是稀奇啊  妈妈竟然会给我们提示
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给认真考虑过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回来了的米内特的奖励哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉妈妈我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  米内特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然发生了逆流  就说明那有到天盖的水车的传送装置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就能从那里去天盖的水车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是路上有很多晶石怪物  不是超危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样就只好放姐姐去当诱饵了
